sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Staff Edit Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open create/update staff page
    UI->>LW: mount(staff)
    LW->>DB: Load staff user and permissions (if existing)
    DB-->>LW: Existing values
    LW-->>UI: Render role/permission form

    User->>UI: Change role
    UI->>LW: updatedRole(value)
    LW-->>UI: Adjust permission defaults/options

    User->>UI: Save staff account
    UI->>LW: save()
    LW->>DB: Validate and insert/update user
    LW->>DB: Replace permission rows for user
    DB-->>LW: Persist completed
    LW-->>UI: Success toast (new: redirect to edit page)
